\end{array}\right]$ &
$x_{8} \left[\begin{array}{ccc}
1 & -1/2 & -1/2 \\
-1/2 & 1/4+3\tilde{\epsilon}-\epsilon & 1/4 \\
1/2 & 1/4 & 1/4
\end{array}\right]$ \\
$x_8 [0+\epsilon]$ &
$x_8 [0+\epsilon+3\tilde{\epsilon}-\epsilon]$ \\
$x_8 [1+\epsilon]$ &
